'''Trader's Grotto''' was a quadrant of [[Realspace/Legends|space]] near [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] and one of the more peaceful areas of space in the [[Tatoo system/Legends|Tatoo system]]. This area was crossed by numerous trade routes and provided safe, speedy travel to and from the [[Tatooine Space Station]].

